quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  4,135,"A wid iumnen! Teddut s lmizan, d inagan n Öebbi, xas $ef yiman nnwen, ne$ imawlan u llzem, ama d ameôkanti, ama d igellil. Izwar iten Öebbi. Ur teddut d lhawiyya, ur twezznem ara. Ma txutlem, ne$ twexxôem, ihi, Öebbi Izga Iéôa ayen txeddmem"
  4,136,"A wid iumnen! Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked Tezmamt id Issers i Umazan iS, akked Tezmamt id Issers, uqbel. Win inekôen Öebbi, lmalayek iS, Tizmamin iS, imazanen iS, akked wass aneggaru, ihi innetlaf ttelfan u$miq"
  4,137,"Ih, wid iumnen, sinna, nekôen, sinna, umnen, sinna, nekôen, sinna, zaden di nnkeô, ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, ur ten Ippawi d ubrid"
  4,138,Becceô ixabiten ar fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan
  4,139,"Wid ipparan ijehliyen d iêbiben, war lmumnin, day ssarmen $uôsen tazmert? Tazmert, s tidep, ar Öebbi yakw"
  4,140,"Ni$ Nessers awen d, di Tezmamt: \"ma teslam la nekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, la ttihin fellasen, ur p$imit yidsen, alamma bedlen ameslay. Mulac a ppilim am nitni\". Öebbi, s tidep, a d Issemlil ixabiten akked ijehliyen di Loahennama, meôôa"
  4,141,"Wid i kwen iquôâan, ma Ifka yawen d Öebbi l$elb, a d inin: \"day ur nella ara yidwen\"? Ma illa wayen rebêen ijehliyen, ad inin: \"day ur nêuôeb ara fellawen, nsellek ikwen si lmumnin\"? Ad Iêudd Öebbi garawen, ass n tnekra. Ur Ippara ara Öebbi, i ijehliyen, abrid ar lmumnin"
  4,142,"Ih, ixabiten xedâen Öebbi. D Neppa iten Ixedâan. Ma kren d i téallit, a d kren d imaâguza, akken kan a ten id walin medden. Cwiî kan id smektayen Öebbi"
  4,143,"Ur banen akka, ne$ akka; $eô wigi, ne$ $eô wiyav. Win Itlef Öebbi ur as teppafev abrid, d awez$i"
  4,144,"A wid iumnen! Ur pparat ijehliyen d iêbiben, war lmumnin. Day teb$am ad aS tefkem, i Öebbi, adabu ibanen, mgal kwen"
  4,145,"Ih, ixabiten di lqaâa n wadda n tmes, ur asen teppafev asettaô"
  4,146,"Kkes ed wid ituben, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, iîîfen di Öebbi, izzazdgen ddin nnsen ar Öebbi. Widak, ad ilin ar lmumnin. Deqqal a d Iawi Öebbi, i lmumnin, arraz ameqwôaêan"
  4,147,"Acu ara Ixdem Öebbi s uâaqeb nnwen, ma tesnemmrem, tumnem? Ni$ Öebbi Ippara tajmilt, Iéôa"